# Access Control Matrix â€“ Healthcare Systems

Access control is the foundation of healthcare data privacy.

## Typical Roles
- Doctor
- Nurse
- Technician
- Billing Staff
- IT Administrator
- Management

## Access Principles
- Least privilege
- Role-based access (RBAC)
- Segregation of duties
- Periodic access review

## Implementation Notes
- Separate clinical and administrative access
- Emergency override (break-glass) mechanisms
- Automatic de-provisioning on exit
